</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="86" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="86">
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Oecophoridae" genus="Hieromantis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hieromantis" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Hieromantis</taxonomicName>
Meyrick, 1897: 315. Type species: 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Oecophoridae" genus="Hieromantis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Hieromantis ephodophora" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ephodophora">Hieromantis ephodophora</taxonomicName>
